Package org.osgi.service.http.whiteboard.propertytypes

Annotation Type HttpWhiteboardFilterRegex

  • @ComponentPropertyType
@Retention(CLASS)
@Target(TYPE)
@RequireHttpWhiteboard
public @interface HttpWhiteboardFilterRegex
    Component Property Type for the osgi.http.whiteboard.filter.regex service property.

    This annotation can be used on a Filter to declare the value of the HTTP_WHITEBOARD_FILTER_REGEX service property.

    Since:
    1.1
